rows.label: qst101502_msg0001
rows.name: Eating my fill... *nom nom*...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0002
rows.name: Drinking my fill... *gulp gulp*...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0003
rows.name:
Sinking into the Cloud
Sea, mo... *burp*...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0101
rows.name:
Momo? Have you found
a Divine Beast, mo?

rows.label: qst101502_msg0102
rows.name: ...It's no use, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0103
rows.name:
Even if there's a Divine Beast, without
a hull, nothing is solved, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0104
rows.name:
The will to build a hull
vanished long ago, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0105
rows.name: You'll build a hull, mo?

rows.label: qst101502_msg0106
rows.name:
In that case... you'll need
to gather the wood, process
it, and assemble it, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0107
rows.name:
You don't have to push
yourself... *hiccup*

rows.label: qst101502_msg0108
rows.name:
My body has gotten quite heavy, mo...
The day Umon becomes debris in the Cloud
Sea is just around the corner, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0201
rows.name:
When I become debris in the
Cloud Sea, so that I can feel
what the sunken ships felt...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0202
rows.name:
I'll just keep eating, mo...
*huff*... *munch munch*...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0301
rows.name: You've come at a good time, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0302
rows.name:
The amount I have to pay is getting to
be... no, I mean, I've reached the weight
to sink into the Cloud Sea, so...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0303
rows.name:
I'll put the bill on Tora's tab
and jump into the Cloud Sea, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0304
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]The hull is complete, mo?!

rows.label: qst101502_msg0305
rows.name:
What in the world, mo! It
was worth the wait...

rows.label: qst101502_msg0306
rows.name:
...*urp* I'll throw up if I
suddenly make a fuss, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0307
rows.name:
If I don't see it with my own
eyes, I can't die in peace, mo.

rows.label: qst101502_msg0308
rows.name:
I'm going to the shipyard right away,
mo! Friends, you come too, mo!
